Rating: 3
This gingerbread cake is very moist and delicious- definitely worth making because it's super easy. However, we didn't think the mascarpone was that good. Instead, I whipped up a 1/2 cup whipping cream until it was stiff, added 1 tablespoon of confectioner's sugar and 1/8 tsp vanilla, whipped it all together and served that as a topping. It was terrific as a tasty and festive Christmas dessert.

